race.description: Scott Ellis Memorial / Ranbuild Warwick Handicap
race.comment: OUTSMARTED (2) is building up an impressive strike rate winning four of six overall and looks the galloper in this line-up with the most upside. Tuned up for this with a recent trial placing and is yet to miss a drum in two fresh attempts. Bold showing expected. BIG BOY GEORGE (4) is a three-time winner over this six-furlong journey and is much better than the past couple of efforts suggest. Worth another chance. MACHINE HEAD (11) has hit the top-four in eight of his past nine starts and is usually thereabouts. A must for the multiples. FAKE MAGIC (1) is a last-start winner who shouldn't be slept on.
